title: Are You Calling the Cops ( Earn Your Leisure)
itunes:title: Are You Calling the Cops ( Earn Your Leisure)
description:
Today on the show we had our friends from Earn your Leisure and Ian Dunlap where they spoke about On Stock Market Patterns, Crypto Futures, Real Estate and more.

Also, Charlamagne gave “Donkey of the day” to an ambulance driver that faces a DUI and homicide charges after wrecking ambulance, killing patient in the back and failing sobriety test. Moreover, we opened the phone lines to see if any of our listeners had to call the cops on their partner based off of Dababy and Dani Leigh’s argument.
